<DOCNO> FBIS3-5537 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas046__a94016" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-046-A </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  9 March 1994 </DATE1>

