  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, March 9 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- The Japanese 
Government renders as a gratis assistance to Mongolia 
agricultural machines and fertilizers for development of 
agricultural production. 
  Thus, in 1953 [year as received] before the sowing works 
Japan has delivered to the country 14 tractors and 500 tonnes of 
fertilizers. Recently more than 20 tractors with ploughs have 
been dispatched from Japan to Mongolia. 

