<F P=102>  SK1003104794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1008 GMT 10 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1003104794 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 10 (KCNA) -- The Federation of 
South Koreans in Japan for Democracy and Unification 
("Hantongnyon") finalized its action program for 1994 at the 
second representative conference held in Tokyo recently. 
  The keynote of the action program is to bring earlier the 
reunification of the country by strengthening great national 
unity, repulse foreign interference and realize national 
independence, peace and denuclearization, t the "National 
Security Law" of South Korea scrapped and urge atonement for the 
history of Japanese imperialist aggression and a settlement of 
the issue of postwar compensation. 

