<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 10 (KCNA) -- The dear leader Comade 
Kim Chong-il received messages of greetings from foreign party 
leaders on the occasion of his birthday. 
  The messages came from Hasanul Huq Inu, general secretary of 
the Central Executive Committee of the Bangladesh National 
Socialist Party; Dogu Ferincek, chairman of the Workers' Party 
of Turkey; Manuel Vargas Loureiro, president of the Democratic 
Renovation Party of Portugal; Vladimir Dado, chairman of the 
